      "name": "PALETTE",
      "file_suffix": "PALETTE_DATA",
      "char_count": 60,
      "layout": "palette table: N rows x 16 colors x 2B ARGB4444 LE, idx0=transparent (PL00 = 57 palettes / 1824 B). Same banks as the PVR skin system."
    },
    {
      "name": "ANIMATION",
      "file_suffix": "ANIMATION_DATA",
      "char_count": 60,
      "layout": "0x000-0x3FF header w/ per-frame durations (03E8=1000); 0x400+ = u32 LE pointer table into EXTRAS (random-access frame index)."
    },
    {
      "name": "EXTRAS",
      "file_suffix": "EXTRAS_DATA",
      "char_count": 60,
      "layout": "sprite-assembly / OAM table: 8-byte records [x:s16][y:s16][tile:u16][attr:u16]; attr=0x00FF = frame terminator; attr bit15=h-flip; low byte = palette row. PL00 = 31 frames, 12-147 parts each."
    },
